heading_s: Google celebrates the Hour of Code 2013 with this tribute to Grace Hopper, one of the very first computer programmers.

Nobel Peace Prize winner Malala Yousafzai challenges girls in every country to try the Hour of Code. In her own words, "Every girl deserves to take part in creating the technology that'll change our world, and change who runs it."
short_heading_s: VIDEO: Malala challenges girls to do the Hour of Code
